                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Starting with heavy attack one (the spin) then following up with heavy attack two (the overhead strike) will deal 24% damage hitting every 0.2 seconds while in the first heavy attack animation, then a single hit dealing 800% damage while in the second heavy attack animation."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
