                  "revisionId": 2688723,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Starting with heavy attack two (the overhead strike) then following up heavy attack one (the spin) will deal 80% damage hitting every 0.2 seconds while in the first heavy attack animation, then a single hit dealing 240% damage while in the second heavy attack animation.."
